%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-Kh%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-qjyFFM43hYrWKw3L9DkOXA">Tặng Vương nhị thập tứ thị ngự Khế tứ thập vận - 贈王二十四侍禦契四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ph%C3%BA-Th%E1%BB%A9/Thu%E1%BB%B5-kh%E1%BB%9Fi-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i/poem-FXkkwaXJGdX-NX6-g0nDbw">Thuỵ khởi thư hoài - 睡起書懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ph%C3%BA-Th%E1%BB%A9/author-cJyRnXqV8KjQY5jLmb3KOA">Phạm Phú Thứ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%C3%BD-th%C3%AC-ca-T%E1%BA%B7ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-V%C4%83n-qu%C3%A1n-b%C3%A1c-s%C4%A9-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ki%E1%BB%81n/poem-3ntr8of8WpqEN_ETWKq8Eg">Tuý thì ca - Tặng Quảng Văn quán bác sĩ Trịnh Kiền - 醉時歌－贈廣文館博士鄭虔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-kinh-ph%C3%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-Ti%C3%AAn-huy%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C5%A9-b%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-qHlDll4qtUH2nCJy2-kR4Q">Tự kinh phó Phụng Tiên huyện vịnh hoài ngũ bách tự - 自京赴奉先縣詠懷五百字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
